'''GLIM'''（Generalized Linear Interactive Modelling）是一款采用[[广义线性模型|广义线性模型]]计算方法的统计软件。它是由英国[[:en:Royal_Statistical_Society|皇家统计学会]]的统计计算工作小组（后更名为GLIM工作组）主任约翰·内尔德发起<ref>
[https://web.archive.org/web/20070221234751/http://www.rss.org.uk/main.asp?page=2128 Royal Statistical Society webpage on Working Parties] (archived Feb 2007)</ref><ref>
{{cite journal |last=Nelder |first=John |authorlink=John Nelder |year=1975 |title=Announcement by the Working Party on Statistical Computing: GLIM (Generalized Linear Interactive Modelling Program) |journal=[[Journal_of_the_Royal_Statistical_Society|Journal of the Royal Statistical Society]]. Series C (Applied Statistics) |volume=24 |issue=2 |pages=259–261 |id= {{JSTOR|2346575}} }}</ref>，并于1974年首次发布。1993年由[[:en:Numerical_Algorithms_Group|Numerical Algorithms Group]]发布了最后的版本（GLIM4）<ref>
{{cite book |title=The GLIM System: Release 4 Manual |url=https://archive.org/details/glimsystemreleas0000unse |first=Brian | last=Francis |coauthors=Mick Green; Clive Payne |year=1993 |publisher=Clarendon Press |location=Oxford |isbn= 0198522312}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nag.co.uk/stats/GDGE_soft.asp |title=NAG webpage for GLIM |accessdate=2009-11-15 |archive-date=2010-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101012041544/http://www.nag.co.uk/stats/GDGE_soft.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 

GLIM被认为是第一个使用[[广义线性模型|广义线性模型]]计算方法的统计软件，并加入了互动，[[迭代|迭代]]方法等统计模型<ref>
{{cite book| title=Statistical Modelling in GLIM | url=https://archive.org/details/statisticalmodel00oces |first=Murray| last=Aitken | coauthors=Dorothy Anderson; Brian Francis; John Hinde| year=1989 | publisher=Oxford University Press| location=Oxford | isbn=0198522037}}</ref>。GLIM使用命令行界面，允许用户定义自己的[[宏|宏模块]]。

GLIM已经不再更新版本。在一些学术研究机构，可能还可以找到装有GLIM的计算机。

